output:
Camping Checklist: 
- Tent 
- Sleeping bag and/or blankets 
- Pillows 
- Camping stove 
- Propane 
- Matches 
- Firewood 
- Cooking supplies (pots, pans, plates, bowls, utensils, etc.) 
- Food & water 
- Flashlight and/or lantern 
- Toiletries (toilet paper, soap, towels, etc.) 
- First aid kit 
- Insect repellent 
- Sunscreen 
- Clothes and shoes 
- Games and books 
- Binoculars 
- Camera 
- Phone and/or map
